mely volatile in 2016, lots of people are hoping the Fed will step in to save the day with&hellip;</p></div></a></div><div class="small-12 medium-6 large-4 columns article-summary"><a href="http://dailyreckoning.com/proof-that-people-are-dumb/"><div class="article-image"><img src="http://dweaay7e22a7h.cloudfront.net/dr-content_3/uploads/2014/11/Umbrella-Pig-225x125.jpg" data-img-src="http://dweaay7e22a7h.cloudfront.net/dr-content_3/uploads/2016/02/LuckyCactus-225x125.jpg"></div><div class="inner-text"><h3>Proof that People are Dumb</h3><div class="meta-text"><p> By Michael Covel Posted February 12, 2016</p></div><p>Michael Covel explains how your personal psychology may get in the way of making money in the markets… and one important concept&hellip;</p></div></a></div><div class="hide-for-medium large-4 columns article-summary"><a href="http://dailyreckoning.com/the-biggest-financial-scam-ever-hint-its-not-madoff/"><div class="article-image"><img src="http://dweaay7e22a7h.cloudfront.net/dr-content_3/uploads/2014/11/Umbrella-Pig-225x125.jpg" data-img-src="http://dweaay7e22a7h.cloudfront.net/dr-content_3/uploads/2016/02/Wall_Street_Sign_1-9-225x125.jpg"></div><div class="inner-text"><h3>The Biggest Financial Scam Ever (Hint: It’s Not Madoff)</h3><div class="meta-text"><p> By Michael Covel Posted February 11, 2016</p></div><p>Michael Covel shares the retirement-killing scam the government, Wall Street, mainstream media, and even the universities are in on&#8230;</p></div></a></div></div></div></li><li><a href="http://dailyreckoning.com/author/chrismayer">Chris Mayer</a><div class="featured-articles"><div class="row collapse"><div class="small-12 medium-6 large-4 columns article-summary"><a href="http://dailyreckoning.com/this-gold-royalty-play-is-a-buy/"><div class="article-image"><img src="http://dweaay7e22a7h.cloudfront.net/dr-content_3/uploads/2014/11/Umbrella-Pig-225x125.jpg" data-img-src="http://dweaay7e22a7h.cloudfront.net/dr-content_3/uploads/2015/12/Gold_Bars-2